						               													<description>ReWording is a postcard word game that is for 2-5 players. Designed by Ian Howard.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this competitive word game, players anagram and embellish words to secure the most points at the end of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, the active player either: adds a new word by writing it in one of 5 sections on the shared postcard board; OR builds on a previously-added word by adding and rearranging letters. A player may instead pass, dropping out of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Once all players have passed, score each section of the board individually. The player with the most words in that section scores 1 point for each word they didn&amp;rsquo;t write. The player with the most points wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
